they have never before been calculated\nin spite of the importance of the subject matter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 Mar 2020 18:00:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 24 Aug 2020 16:06:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-25"}
